bilingual.source: Melting ice caps aren't the only factor.

bilingual.source: Another factor behind football's global popularity is the creativity and excitement on the field.

bilingual.source: Independence is an important factor for success.

list.abstract: Factor（英 [ˈfæktə]，美 [ˈfæktər]），英语单词，作名词用，为因素；要素；系数。作动词用，为让售；将…卖给代理商。短语搭配有external factor（外部因素）。例句为“Physical resemblance between people was not a factor.（人与人之间的外貌相似不是一个因素）”。 Factor名词类近义词有element、deputy、agent等，复数形式为factors。
提出rFactor, 新赛跑的模仿系列从图像空间被合并。 在成功地创造在十二产品以后在过去十年， 图像空间采取下个逻辑步骤， 创造一个完全地新技术基地和发展过程。 这个新isiMotor 2.0 环境将是修造扣人心弦的产品许多年来的基础。

yingyinNormal.en: Ice loss to the West Antarctic Ice Sheet has increased by a factor of three on a yearly basis since 2009.
yingyinNormal.zh: 西南极冰盖自2009年起，基于三个因素，每年融冰都增加。

yingyinNormal.en: And in the case of Aerotyne, based on every technical factor out there, John, we are looking at a grand slam home run.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就安若坦来说，综合其中所有的技术因素，John可以期待这会是一记全垒打。

yingyinNormal.en: Of all the things to factor in when running an economy, the most troublesome is people. Now, by and large, humans are a rational lot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在影响经济的所有因素里，最麻烦的就是人。大致上来说，人们是很理性的。

yingyinNormal.en: We've all heard about the computer simulations and now we are watching actual sims. But I can't quite believe you still have not taken into account the human factor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都听说过计算机模拟，现在也看了实际的模拟演示，可让我惊讶的是你们仍然没有把人类因素考虑进去。

yingyinNormal.en: Is that a relevant factor? Yes. Then I suppose you could've agreed to go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这跟伤害她有什么关系？当然有。那我想你应该答应她去的。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy, I was off by a factor of 10,000. But the Chinese team found the element.
yingyinNormal.zh: Amy 我算差了十万八千里，但中国团队发现了那个元素。

yingyinNormal.en: I apologized. I've miscalculated. I forgot to factor in the traffic. 19 minutes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我算错了。我忘了把堵车时间算进去。19分半。

yingyinNormal.en: How's his I.N.R.? The last one was 6. Okay, give him factor VII, F.F.P.s and platelets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的血凝度是多少？上一次测量是6。给他输第七凝血因子，冷冻血浆和血小板。

yingyinNormal.en: Because I do really enjoy that. I also really enjoy the amount I get paid. So we should probably factor that in, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我很喜欢这样，我也很满意我的薪资水平，所以我们应该也把这考虑在内。

yingyinNormal.en: TARS, factor an orbit of Gargantua. Conserve fuel, minimize thrusting, but make sure we stay in range of Miller's planet. You got it?
yingyinNormal.zh: TARS，找一条卡冈图亚的轨道，节省燃料，少用推进器，但要确保在Miller星球的范围内，明白吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Over the last four decades, they've built chips that are ever smaller and ever more powerful, increasing the strength of our computers by a factor of 1 million.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在过去的八十年里他们建造的芯片是越来越小越来越强大，计算机的性能增强了一百万倍。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: A variety of <highlight>factors</highlight> contribute to the long-run increase in the share of young adults living with the parents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多种因素造成了年轻人与父母同住比例的长期增长。

examination_example.sentence: Economic <highlight>factors</highlight> seem to explain less of why young adult women are increasingly likely to live at home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 经济因素似乎不能很好地解释为什么年轻成年女性越来越有可能住在父母家里。
